headline: Meet the Monster Stock That Continues to Crush the Market
summary: Monster Beverage has grown its top line at a 20% compound annual growth rate for 30 years, helping it become the top stock over that time.  In 1997, it launched its first energy drink back when there really wasn't even an energy-drink category.
